snippet.title: Exanima - A Prelude to Sui Generis - Beta Gameplay
snippet.description:
Exanima has now been Greenlit, thank you for your support!

Some gameplay footage from our first beta release of Exanima. Exanima is a prelude to Sui Generis, it is a smaller but complete game set in the underworld of Sui Generis some 20 years prior to its events.

Find out more: http://baremettle.com/

Download/watch a higher quality version here: http://dl.baremettle.com/ExanimaBG.mp4
